 Departments are used to classified tickets. The first step in  user ticket 
submission process is to choose their department. Admin users select department 
in filter option to grab the user posted tickets.Common departments are Sales, 
Support, Billing etc...
{note}

To setup departments, go to configuration > Support > 
Departments.When creating a department you can enter a name and description. 
Those created departments are displaying to users automatically. 

{note}